{"tid":1320293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋只要打贏仗，就會有藍絲支持！","createTime":"2019-07-15T10:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T15:31:28.000Z","uid":260988,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6d484a47f4ec792a8f44b7f9c1287c20a6e87224","tid":1320293,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"部份<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">建制支持者</span></span></span><span style=\"color: teal;\">欺善怕惡</span>，係因為佢哋覺得<span style=\"color: teal;\">搵錢重要過公義</span>，聽惡人話就搵到錢<br />\n<br />\n佢哋認為示威者收錢出嚟，亦係同一原因<br />\n<br />\n但當佢哋認知<span style=\"color: orange;\">抗爭者</span>為公義會拋頭顱灑熱血，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不怕危險</span></span>面對建制傭兵（警察），甚至<span style=\"color: red;\">強勢對抗</span>建制支持者，冇腰骨嘅佢哋就慢慢認知，<span style=\"color: orange;\">要賺錢就要買抗爭者怕</span>，因為<span style=\"color: gold;\">腰骨唔重要，賺錢養家先重要</span><br />\n<br />\n搵錢為上嘅人，要得到佢哋支持，只需表現強勢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">祝大家武運昌隆</span></span>"},{"pid":"84e6c3e3b938e30b0cb7c0d5d3597fe2d10c0fec","tid":1320293,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"4727e6fbfeea39cd616373f39327a9993f845b41","tid":1320293,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"力推"},{"pid":"ea8bebe8bd7605c0b66cf9246e8fe419e2da44c8","tid":1320293,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b59aaeeb360c6e5303a836b4dd42761e5d0e4a87","tid":1320293,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:00:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cba4b250a87ab05b43914a25af3fb34a77a1ce8","tid":1320293,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbab720d45ba0e4bd6ee235eabfcb2841b51a2c4","tid":